# 🗂 Flask CRUD REST API

## 📖 Project Overview
This project demonstrates a simple **REST API** built using **Flask** and **SQLite**.  
The API allows users to **Create, Read, Update, and Delete (CRUD)** items in a database.  
Each item has a `name` and `description`. This project showcases the ability to develop a basic backend API using Python and Flask.

---

## 🧰 Tech Used
- Python 3.x  
- Flask  
- Flask-RESTful  
- Flask-SQLAlchemy  
- SQLite (for database)

